@mboehm7 In RewriteRemovePersistentReadWrite, I've tried things such as the following without success:

```
case PERSISTENTREAD:
    if( _inputs.contains(dop.getName()) ) {
        dop.setDataOpType(DataOpTypes.TRANSIENTREAD);
        if (hop.getDataType() == DataType.SCALAR) {
            dop.setFileName(null);
            dop.getInput().set(dop.getParameterIndex("iofilename"), new LiteralOp(null));
        }
    }
```

Also, such things as
`dop.getInput().set(dop.getParameterIndex("iofilename"), new LiteralOp(Double.NaN));`
and
`dop.getInput().set(dop.getParameterIndex("iofilename"), new LiteralOp(""));`

Do you have any further advice?

@mboehm7 Let me know if the current implementation looks OK. Updated to:

```
if (hop.getDataType() == DataType.SCALAR) {
    int iofilenameIndex = dop.getParameterIndex("iofilename");
    dop.getInput().remove(iofilenameIndex);
    HashMap<String, Integer> parameterIndexMap = dop.getParameterIndexMap();
    parameterIndexMap.remove("iofilename");
    parameterIndexMap.put("format", iofilenameIndex);
}
```
